author: Kimberly (Stylish Sidekick)
title: Evenflo Convertible High Chair Only $29.88 (Regularly $60)
text:
In need of a high chair? Hop on over to Walmart or Amazon where you can score this Evenflo Convertible High Chair for only $29.88 (reg. $60). This high chair transitions from a traditional high chair to a toddler chair & table set and can support children up to 40lbs. Seems like a great deal as Target has this item priced at $39.99!
